{"tid":2315609,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"薛丁格的銀行戶口(Schrödinger's bank account)","createTime":"2020-12-07T09:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:47:07.000Z","uid":193642,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d840deba9b2bb721551b53ed805be5219c1ddb2e","tid":2315609,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"把一個銀行戶口、一個裝有香港警察的玻璃燒瓶和放射性物質放進封閉的盒子裏。當盒子內的監控器偵測到衰變粒子時，就會打破燒瓶，凍結這個銀行戶口。根據量子力學的哥本哈根詮釋，在實驗進行一段時間後，銀行戶口會處於又可用又凍結的疊加態。可是，假若實驗者觀察盒子內部，他會觀察到一個可用戶口或一個凍結戶口，而不是同時處於可用狀態與凍結狀態的貓。這事實引起一個謎題：到底量子疊加是在甚麼時候終止，並且塌縮成兩種可能狀態中的一種狀態？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dd8718dc3b98053d20734de94432eea01b6fbb","tid":2315609,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65f6e798527363a23f8f3b2f35c3837406ec743","tid":2315609,"uid":745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"好難"},{"pid":"bde0027623a1dd182928c01444098f3ff4465cba","tid":2315609,"uid":3441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:45:46.000Z","msg":"你取代漏咗一個貓字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e82583793e81e671d7ef91a71c511d22d000d40","tid":2315609,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"